程式碼與解釋：
https://github.com/b09505030/ahoy/blob/eccaff3d24f1bfc641c9008b2ec0f83d8dbb9e82/permutation%20and%20combination%20in%20c%E6%8E%92%E5%88%97%E7%B5%84%E5%90%88%E5%9C%A8c%E8%AA%9E%E8%A8%80%E4%B8%AD


輸入範例：
input

Enter n: 5 
Enter r: 3
output

Permutation = 60
Combination = 10


Enter the size of array :4
1 2 3 4
Enter the range of array for combination :2
